OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA largely
OL,6,Fdry night with clear spells, possibly
OL,7,Fallowing a few mist patches to
OL,8,Fdevelop. Outbreaks of rain potentially
OL,9,Farriving in the west to end the night,
OL,10,Falong with low cloud pushing into some
OL,11,Fcoasts.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FA bright start in the east,
OL,14,Fbut rather cloudy with showery
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain further west. The
OL,16,Fshowers becoming more widespread into
OL,17,Fthe afternoon, and turning persistent
OL,18,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
